<tr>
<td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4de.png" alt="📞" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 24/7 Customer Support</td>
<td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Look for platforms with round-the-clock support to answer questions and resolve issues promptly.</td>
