<td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f510.png" alt="🔐" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Strong Security Measures</td>
